Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.07,0:23:51.08,Scr,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@HYQiHei 65S\frz-90\fscx90\fscy90\c&H000000&\pos(112.001,110.667)}都说了这怎么可能啊
